{"ID":"20240201213722-jzyxisi","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240201213722-jzyxisi","title":"high-availability-system-design","updated":"20240201213722"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213723-qzvgv90","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20240201213723-qzvgv90","updated":"20240201213723"}},{"ID":"20240201213724-j0pyjc9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213724-j0pyjc9","updated":"20240201213724"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"title: 高可用系统设计指南"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"category: 高可用"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"icon: design"}]},{"ID":"20240201213725-qrmsb14","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20240201213725-qrmsb14","updated":"20240201213725"}},{"ID":"20240201213726-raaph52","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213726-raaph52","updated":"20240201213726"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是高可用？可用性的判断标准是啥？"}]},{"ID":"20240201213727-uh48xr3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213727-uh48xr3","updated":"20240201213727"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"高可用描述的是一个系统在大部分时间都是可用的，可以为我们提供服务的。高可用代表系统即使在发生硬件故障或者系统升级的时候，服务仍然是可用的。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213728-7zw5muv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213728-7zw5muv","updated":"20240201213728"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一般情况下，我们使用多少个 9 来评判一个系统的可用性，比如 99.9999% 就是代表该系统在所有的运行时间中只有 0.0001% 的时间是不可用的，这样的系统就是非常非常高可用的了！当然，也会有系统如果可用性不太好的话，可能连 9 都上不了。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213729-j92odux","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213729-j92odux","updated":"20240201213729"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除此之外，系统的可用性还可以用某功能的失败次数与总的请求次数之比来衡量，比如对网站请求 1000 次，其中有 10 次请求失败，那么可用性就是 99%。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213730-vj1m5zm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213730-vj1m5zm","updated":"20240201213730"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"哪些情况会导致系统不可用？"}]},{"ID":"20240201213731-9c3cwov","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213731-9c3cwov","updated":"20240201213731"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213732-8j1fmf9","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213732-8j1fmf9","updated":"20240201213732"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213733-iz1u524","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213733-iz1u524","updated":"20240201213733"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"黑客攻击；"}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213734-9vbcgil","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213734-9vbcgil","updated":"20240201213734"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213735-yoc9q9o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213735-yoc9q9o","updated":"20240201213735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"硬件故障，比如服务器坏掉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213736-ytd69d6","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213736-ytd69d6","updated":"20240201213736"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213737-fdlpj3h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213737-fdlpj3h","updated":"20240201213737"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"并发量/用户请求量激增导致整个服务宕掉或者部分服务不可用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213738-57w1srh","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NA==","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213738-57w1srh","updated":"20240201213738"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213739-j995vre","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240